---
// src/components/Hero.astro
---
<section class="relative bg-white pt-20 pb-32 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center relative z-10">
    
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-edurun-blue/10 border border-edurun-blue/20 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 mb-8">
      <span class="flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-edurun-blue"></span>
      <span class="text-sm font-medium text-edurun-blue tracking-wide">Compatible con Canvas LTI 1.3</span>
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold text-edurun-dark tracking-tight mb-6">
      Integridad académica <br class="hidden md:block" />
      <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-edurun-blue to-edurun-purple">
        sin compromisos.
      </span>
    </h1>

    <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-xl text-gray-500 mb-10">
      Edurun es el entorno de evaluación para Python que mitiga el uso de IA mediante trazabilidad avanzada y contenedores seguros.
    </p>

    <div class="flex justify-center gap-4">
      <a href="#contacto" class="bg-edurun-dark text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold hover:bg-gray-900 transition-all shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-1">
        Solicitar Demo
      </a>
      <a href="/docs/arquitectura" class="bg-white text-edurun-dark border border-gray-200 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold hover:bg-gray-50 transition-all">
        Ver Documentación
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 w-full -translate-x-1/2 h-full z-0 pointer-events-none">
    <div class="absolute top-20 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-edurun-blue/20 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-30 mix-blend-multiply animate-blob"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-20 right-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-edurun-purple/20 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-30 mix-blend-multiply animate-blob animation-delay-2000"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes blob {
    0% { transform: translate(0px, 0px) scale(1); }
    33% { transform: translate(30px, -50px) scale(1.1); }
    66% { transform: translate(-20px, 20px) scale(0.9); }
    100% { transform: translate(0px, 0px) scale(1); }
  }
  .animate-blob {
    animation: blob 7s infinite;
  }
  .animation-delay-2000 {
    animation-delay: 2s;
  }
</style>